<title>USA: NationsBank creates direct-sales unit.</title>
<headline>NationsBank creates direct-sales unit.</headline>
<dateline>CHARLOTTE, N.C. 1996-10-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>NationsBank Corp said on Thursday it is creating a national direct-sales unit and increased the hours of operations at its Richmond customer-service call center.</p>
<p>The new direct-sales unit will create up to 300 full- and part-time jobs, the company said.</p>
<p>The moves are being made in an effort to increase customer access to its products and services, it said.  </p>
<p>The company said it recently expanded the hours of its customer-service operations to 24 hours a day, seven days a week.</p>
<p>Before the change, the center was open from 7 a.m. to 10 p.m., Monday through Friday, and from 9 a.m. to 1 p.m. on Saturday.</p>
